{"tid":352720,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【時薪幾百變5位數】擺合照上網爆紅有前科 揭電競女神Rose Ma極速上位路","createTime":"2017-08-09T03:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T09:45:58.000Z","uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9afe6c294bef6a71df61fa083976a6edae3e9085","tid":352720,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:52:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/finance/20170809/537430\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Ffinance%2F20170809%2F537430&d=K7m9CDySsgaXUDngZw04526tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=1d5560dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Ffinance%2F20170809%2F537430&h=4e2ae002\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/finance/20170809/537430</a><br />\n<br />\n要數到近期最紅的KOL，當然是「一post成名」的Rose Ma(馬俊怡)。其實她由普通show girl上位到「電競女神」，只是用了兩年時間。在她未上位前，更曾受過「慈母」警棍「保護」。<br />\n<br />\nRose Ma事跡早見於2013年，當時她參加FACE UStar校花校草選舉，正報讀媒體高級文憑，更自稱做過楊冪秀髮替身。雖然不入十大，但仍活躍於模特兒工作。到2015年，她參加由電競設備生產商組成的女子電競隊，但坦言只出賽過一次：「有同台灣女子孩打過一次，但係輸咗，之後有就無參加過比賽，就自己開台打機<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n之後她乘電競熱潮，繼續在電玩展上擔任show girl，因其大眼及豐滿身材令她極速上位。今年更遠赴美國拉斯維加斯出席EVO 2017比賽活動，其中與美國著名電競選手Justin Wong的合照，因Justin擺出半個心心手勢，但穿著「春麗裝」的Rose就只以「like」手勢回敬。 <br />\n<br />\n照片吸引多名日本網友「改圖」，「撮合」他們擺出心心手勢，事件更令Rose在twitter爆紅。好就指：「本身都係因為男朋友，所以先結識到佢哋（梅原大吾及Justin Wong），佢哋兩個都喺電競界比較知名，即係 大家知道係玩嘅，影咗張相，我都無諗過twitter會瘋傳。」 <br />\n<br />\n早已公開電競選手HumanBomb為男友的Rose，未有因此失去Fans的支持，早前動漫電玩節更成為最具話題的cosplayer，但她對網上爭議不欲多談，表示只想事件快點完結。"},{"pid":"b151317965c7c4c9338e3f749b18733f13f5a436","tid":352720,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T08:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9203d51f9c9f292f28a553a0431a2e636799fd88","tid":352720,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T08:39:10.000Z","msg":"要多謝distance"},{"pid":"6db1dea3eae90ea50f42254aebd3ad94b20579c7","tid":352720,"uid":20428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T09:40:18.000Z","msg":"佢真係好似明日花 抵佢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c337ef4c8dcde1c8d23eb4c792b35d3213e8cbe","tid":352720,"uid":123224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T09:41:51.000Z","msg":"其實個樣唔係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c132364fba77ba644185355fc6727ee44dc7c64","tid":352720,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T09:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實個樣唔係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直頭唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}